  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"/assets/library/exaone3.5/fb3ee4b4-a180-4d81-8896-fef74b2e1662\" width=\"300\"/></p>\n\n<p>EXAONE 3.5 is a collection of instruction-tuned bilingual (English and Korean) generative models ranging from 2.4B to 32B parameters, developed and released by LG AI Research. EXAONE 3.5 language models include:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>2.4B model optimized for deployment on small or resource-constrained devices</li>\n<li>7.8B model matching the size of its predecessor but offering improved performance</li>\n<li>32B model delivering powerful performance.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>All models support long-context processing of up to 32K tokens. Each model demonstrates state-of-the-art performance in real-world use cases and long-context understanding, while remaining competitive in general domains compared to recently released models of similar sizes.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/assets/library/exaone3.5/e01a3df2-72b4-408b-bae8-975e59821303\" alt=\"benchmarks\"/></p>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.04862\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paper</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/LGAI-EXAONE/exaone-35-674d0e1bb3dcd2ab6f39dbb4\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugging Face</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.lgresearch.ai/blog/view?seq=507\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blog</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
